<div class='app-card-container'>
  <div class='card'>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class='row'>
      <div class='col-md-4'>
        <%= image_tag 'profile_image.jpg', width: 300, alt: 'Profile Image' %>

        <div class='skills'>
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class='skill'>
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class='progress'>
                <div 
                  class='pregress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning'
                  role='pregressbar'
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax='100'
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                    
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='col-md-8'>
        <p>I am a fullstack developer, specializing in React.JS and Redux on frontend side and in Ruby on Rails on backend side.</p>
        <p>My development pattern is focused on communication. When I take on a project not only do I work to craft the application according to the client's specifications, I give daily updates to ensure that the project is aligning properly with the client's goals. The end result is the right product, delivered on time, and on budget.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#jobHistory'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='jobHistory'
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class='btn btn-primary'
            type='button'
            data-toggle='collapse'
            data-target='#education'
            aria-expanded='false'
            aria-controller='education'
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class='collapse' id='jobHistory'>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL JOB #1
            </div>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL JOB #2
            </div>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL JOB #3
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='collapse' id='education'>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL School #1
            </div>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL School #2
            </div>
            <div class='card card-block'>
              REALLY COOL School #3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>